726514f-b.title: Queens: Dry Harbor Road - 82nd Street
726514f-b.text:
Dry Harbor Road, west side, at 82nd Street. This house is
in the line of 82nd Street at its point of intersection with Dry
Harbor Road. Mrs. Seits or Seites was the owner in 1873. The
later view of this set shows the building being repaired.
1923
View 2: May 1926
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection

726512f-a.title: Queens: Dry Harbor Road - 82nd Place
726512f-a.text:
Dry Harbor Road, east from 82nd .Place. The land on which
the frame dwellings stand, on the north side of the road, was
owned by Fred Jurgens in 1909.
July 2, 1935
P. L. Sperr
